*rsstail-1.3 (25 Aug 2007)

  25 Aug 2007; Wulf C. Krueger <philantrop@gentoo.org> +rsstail-1.3.ebuild:
  Version bump to 1.3 as requested by rbu.
  Upstream changes:
  - added switch that limits the amount of text displayed
  - added switch which prevents rsstail from aborting when an error occurs
  - fixed segfault on FreeBSD
  - man page added

